A no-fuss essential that feels good and lasts.

Rep your favorite chew brand in style with the official Mumbies tee. Made from ultra-soft, breathable cotton and screen printed with our signature logo, this shirt is built for comfort and made to last—just like our chews. Whether you’re out on a walk, lounging with your pup, or hitting the farmer’s market, the deep Midnight Blue and clean white print make it easy to wear anywhere. It’s the kind of shirt you’ll reach for again and again—and hey, your dog might even approve.

T-shirt style: Regular mens/unisex fit, mid-weight 5.3 oz / 180 GSM, 100 % combed cotton, pre-shrunk to keep its shape. 

Print: Crisp white mumbies logo, screen-printed front and centre for a clean, durable finish.

Build: Neck ribbing, shoulder-to-shoulder tape, side seams and double-needle hems add everyday strength and comfort. 

Color: Midnight Blue — deep navy that pairs with anything.

Care:
  • Machine wash cold with like colours.
  • Do not bleach.
  • Do not tumble dry.
  • Do not dry clean.
  • Do not iron if printed.
  • Line dry in shade.
